sql: /* HyperEVM DEX - USDH Daily Trading Volume by Project (Sep 15, 2025 onwards) */ SELECT DATE_TRUNC('DAY', block_timestamp) AS date, project, COUNT(*) AS trade_count, COUNT(DISTINCT transaction_from_address) AS unique_traders, SUM(usd_amount) AS trading_volume_usd, SUM(CASE WHEN token_sold_address = LOWER('0x111111a1a0667d36bD57c0A9f569b98057111111') THEN usd_amount ELSE 0 END) AS usdh_sold_volume, SUM(CASE WHEN token_bought_address = LOWER('0x111111a1a0667d36bD57c0A9f569b98057111111') THEN usd_amount ELSE 0 END) AS usdh_bought_volume FROM hyperevm.dex.trades WHERE (token_sold_address = LOWER('0x111111a1a0667d36bD57c0A9f569b98057111111') OR token_bought_address = LOWER('0x111111a1a0667d36bD57c0A9f569b98057111111')) AND block_timestamp >= CAST('2025-09-15' AS DATE) GROUP BY 1, 2 ORDER BY date ASC, project LIMIT 1000
